            <Heading/>
            <Record>
                <Paragraph MissionStatmentId="154" SortOrder="1">The Bureau of Ocean Energy Management manages development of U.S. Outer Continental Shelf energy and mineral resources in a way that is environmentally and economically responsible.</Paragraph>
